<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-23-0437 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper gives a brief overview of how Esso utilizes computer systemsto generate contracts in dilling services. The benefits of the systeminclude an immediate reduction in support staff, job enhancement, reducedprocess time, the ability to share contract information among users,an increased ability to respond to peak loads and an effective promotionamong users, and increased ability to respond to peak loads and an effectivepromotion of contract standardization and procedural consistency. Thesebenefits make it possible to produce high quality contracts while reducingcosts. 1 tab., 4 figs.</TEXT></DOC>